title: Here Is the Dude Tex Is Fighting At Rough N Rowdy: Chris “In It To Win It” Bennett
text:
Email 
Ok I’m calling bullshit here. The promoter of Rough N Rowdy kind of rigged this against our boy. I’ve been to Rough N Rowdy. Nobody can fight. That’s why I thought it would be great for Tex to enter this thing. I mean there was one legit knockout in the entire 50 fights I witnessed. Every other fight was guys getting tired and split decisions. Unfortunately (or fortunately depending on how you look at it) the promoter put Tex in the ring with the guy who had the major knockout. Dude is a borderline professional tough man fighter/pro mma guy. He’s got his own fight channel on youtube. Just a dirtbag move to stick Tex in the ring vs. a boderline pro. I wouldn’t even care if Tex said fuck it I’m not going. But we all know Tex ain’t scared of shit so he still wants a piece of this dude. Nuts dragging on the ground. And guess what? I think he’s gonna fucking shock the world. Don’t know how, don’t know why, but like Tex said he’s due for a W. El Presidente |
